ictk.boardgame.chess.net.ics.event
Class ICSSeekRemoveEvent

java.lang.Object
  ictk.boardgame.chess.net.ics.event.ICSEvent
      ictk.boardgame.chess.net.ics.event.ICSSeekRemoveEvent
public class ICSSeekRemoveEvent
extends ICSEvent

This message from the server indicates that a number of seek ads should be cleared from the client's records. The server does not keep track of which seeks you know about though.
